# Nodjirambaye Eric — AI, Economics & Education

> **Using AI, Data & Education to Create Social Impact Across Africa**

## About This Platform

This is the source code for my personal research and portfolio website, built to serve as:
- A **research hub** for my work on AI, labor markets, and digital policy in West Africa
- A **technical portfolio** showcasing data science and Python projects
- An **educational resource** for African students pursuing AI, data science, and international scholarships
- A **professional identity** connecting my interdisciplinary background in economics, education, and technology

## Who I Am

- **Economist & AI Researcher** — BSc Economics, researching AI's impact on youth employment in Nigeria
- **Educator** — 10+ years teaching experience, FLE-certified (Institut français), British Council ESL-certified
- **Data Practitioner** — Python, SQL, data visualization, building tools for low-connectivity environments
- **Dual Citizen** — Chad & Nigeria, bridging Francophone and Anglophone African perspectives

