## Featured Projects

- **Nigeria Inflation Dashboard** — Interactive visualization of inflation trends (2010–2023)
- **Offline Voice Assistant** — Python/Kivy Android app for low-connectivity environments
- **AI Employment Impact Analyzer** — Toolkit supporting OMEE research paper
- **SQL Case Studies Collection** — Real-world scenarios for data science education

